lead_paragraph: The European Tour is introducing the Rolex Series this year, which starts in late May with the BMW PGA Championship at Wentworth and ends in late November with the season-ending DP World Tour Championship in Dubai.

headline.print_headline: World Ranking Gap Widens Between US and Europe
